Founded in 1937, Ampacet Corporation is a leading global masterbatch supplier committed to designing innovative custom colors, high performance additive solutions, multipurpose whites and blacks as well as sustainable masterbatches. 

With a strong commitment to technological advancement and customer-driven innovation, Ampacet serves a wide array of industries across the plastics value chain.
