 Ampacet is deeply committed to sustainability, consistently developing environmentally responsible solutions to address both environmental and societal challenges. Its growing portfolio of sustainable products reflects its proactive role in promoting circular economy practices and reducing environmental impact.
 Demonstrating its focus on specialized markets, Ampacet has recently introduced ELTech™ masterbatches, engineered to meet the specific performance and compliance requirements of the Electrical & Electronic Equipment (E&E) sector.

Additionally, the company has launched the ProVital™ range, a line of masterbatches designed for medical applications. These formulations are developed using pre-tested raw materials to support compliance with ISO 10993 biocompatibility standards and European Pharmacopoeia requirements, helping customers navigate stringent regulatory demands.
