PREMIUM
High-tech machines to produce plastic and laminated tube packaging—primarily used in the cosmetics, pharmaceutical, food, and personal care sectors—are our area of expertise. With over 60 years, AISA Automation Industrielle SA stands out for its know-how in development and manufacturing, industrial automation, integrating artificial intelligence into production processes, and its ability to deliver innovative, and eco-conscious solutions in the tube packaging equipment to an international clientele.
From cosmetics to food applications, Aisa, a Swiss family-owned company, offers one of the most complete and reliable ranges of tube-making machines and lines in the industry, with a comprehensive portfolio suitable for all types of products, materials, and production speeds. Whether you’re a small startup or a large-scale manufacturer with high-volume needs, we provide tailored solutions to meet your specific tube packaging requirements.
